- Define schemas for all data structures to ensure type safety and validation
- Use Zod's built-in validation methods for common data types and patterns
- Implement custom validation logic using Zod's refine and superRefine methods
- Utilize Zod's infer utility to generate TypeScript types from schemas
- Use Zod's async parsing capabilities for validating asynchronous data